{"tid":105482,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Cara怎麼可以這麼帥！5 位你可能沒想到他們也會 Beatbox 的大明星！","createTime":"2017-02-03T02:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T06:54:35.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be59ecad0980be2b95e0f71191737d35ad33b507","tid":105482,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:37:17.000Z","msg":"許多明星時常會展現令我們出乎意料的才能，這一次我們就要盤點那一些意外會「Beatbox」口技才能的藝人，如果你以為 Beatbox 其實很簡單，不妨跟著下面的影片一起模仿看看，就知道這一些大明星可不是隨便獻技的！<br />\n<br />\n▼卡拉&middot;迪樂芬妮（Cara Delevingne）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62255/5893e1d3047b4.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62255%2F5893e1d3047b4.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a830035d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國超模近年轉戰電影圈成功，同時她也時常秀出自己的 Beatbox 才能，也曾經秀過打鼓技巧，讓人懷疑這位年輕超模是不是真的十項全能？<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62255/5893e06dcbefe.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62255%2F5893e06dcbefe.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=4cd2f42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼很多人應該都看過卡拉上脫口秀的 Beatbox 影片，小編這裡選出卡拉在宣傳電影《紙上城市》（Paper Towns），與男主角納特&middot;沃爾夫（Nat Wolff）合作的可愛短片，就知道卡拉私底下一定超愛這樣玩。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R0pk20DO6qk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR0pk20DO6qk&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c7fbd83d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R0pk20DO6qk</a><br />\n<br />\n▼肖恩&middot;曼德斯（Shawn Mendes）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62255/5893e072c2f9b.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62255%2F5893e072c2f9b.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=fd4ba761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不用懷疑為什麼這麼多人迷戀這位 18 歲的加拿大歌手，肖恩&middot;曼德斯不只外表俊俏可愛，性格上也是溫暖的陽光大男孩，這讓許多聽眾可能一時聯想不動肖恩&middot;曼德斯其實也會酷酷的 Beatbox。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dLWZ_TwZr7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdLWZ_TwZr7M&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a1244e3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dLWZ_TwZr7M</a><br />\n<br />\n▼查理&middot;普斯（Charlie Puth）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62255/5893e65e7ff68.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62255%2F5893e65e7ff68.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=9162402f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時常被粉絲暱稱為「斷眉」的查理&middot;普斯，也曾經當眾前秀出自己即興的 Beatbox 技能。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QT89VymaMUg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQT89VymaMUg&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=aa68a40c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QT89VymaMUg</a><br />\n<br />\n▼威爾史密斯（Will Smith）早在年輕時就於節目上秀出自己的口技才能，之後參加脫口秀主持人吉米法隆（Jimmy Fallon）節目又再秀了一次。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5w7VNmIJf8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5w7VNmIJf8U&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7869b180\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5w7VNmIJf8U</a><br />\n<br />\n最後看到加拿大超人氣歌手Justin Bieber曾經展現 Rap 和 Beatbox 的影片，早期的他時常會在現場演唱中加入口技，現在則鮮少再聽到小賈斯汀的 Beatbox 。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5qESy23bZlQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5qESy23bZlQ&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b1783b50\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5qESy23bZlQ</a>"},{"pid":"57e98f63dc5efe4ef26cc4d15e4819a4bd428cb2","tid":105482,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"朱千雪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}